title: 133: Solving Your Strange Job Problems (Fan Questions)| Ear Biscuits Ep. 133
description:
Learn to work that alter ego when faced with a boss who can't remember your name. R&L give valuable advice to the Mythical Beasts' work issues ranging from constantly singing coworkers to chronically whistling noses and more on this episode of Ear Biscuits.
